ch of how author's inscriptive reality appears in the world.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Jun 2024) 0aNothing (Philosophy). 0aPerspective (Philosophy). 0aWhole and parts (Philosophy). 4aLiterature : Literary Theory. 4aPhilosophy : Philosophy. 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package 2016z978311149098440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781438459813423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781438459813/original  a978-3-11-149098-4  SUNY Press eBook Package 2016b2016  aGBV-deGruyter-alles